== Overview ==
The AR-888 Shatter Cannon is designed to destroy Federate armored units with devastating blasts. Its disadvantages are a slow arming delay and lack of shield penetration.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Shatter Cannon can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
